    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [c.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[TagId]
FROM [ProductTags] AS [c.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[Id], [t8].[Id0], [c.Product.ProductCategory.Products0].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [Products] AS [c.Product.ProductCategory.Products0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [c5].[Id], [c.Product.ProductCategory5].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [BillDetails] AS [c5]
        INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [c.Size5] ON [c5].[SizeId] = [c.Size5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Products] AS [c.Product5] ON [c5].[ProductId] = [c.Product5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [c.Product.ProductCategory5] ON [c.Product5].[CategoryId] = [c.Product.ProductCategory5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c.Color5] ON [c5].[ColorId] = [c.Color5].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [c.Bill5] ON [c5].[BillId] = [c.Bill5].[Id]
        WHERE [c5].[BillId] = @__billId_0
    ) AS [t8] ON [c.Product.ProductCategory.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t8].[Id0]
) AS [t9] ON [c.Product.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t9].[Id1]
ORDER BY [t9].[Id], [t9].[Id0], [t9].[Id1]" (0723d8ff)

    WHEN [c.Product.ProductTags].[TagId] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [c.Product.ProductTags].[TagId]
FROM [ProductTags] AS [c.Product.ProductTags]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c6].[Id], [c.Product6].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [c6]
    INNER JOIN [Sizes] AS [c.Size6] ON [c6].[SizeId] = [c.Size6].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [c.Product6] ON [c6].[ProductId] = [c.Product6].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [c.Product.ProductCategory6] ON [c.Product6].[CategoryId] = [c.Product.ProductCategory6].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c.Color6] ON [c6].[ColorId] = [c.Color6].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Bills] AS [c.Bill6] ON [c6].[BillId] = [c.Bill6].[Id]
    WHERE [c6].[BillId] = @__billId_0
) AS [t10] ON [c.Product.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t10].[Id0]
ORDER BY [t10].[Id], [t10].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)
